**Platform:** Windows

**Description:**  
Rush Set Go is a fun game for Windows where you need to stay alive in a tough world. You control your character with simple moves like going right or left. Along the way, you'll face dangers like obstacles, but you can also find helpful things like food and coins. The more you move forward and collect coins, the better your score gets. The game looks really cool with its 3D graphics, and it gets more challenging as you go on.
